<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.5">
<l>villār viḻavil vaṭamaturai virumpi virumpā mallaṭarttu</l>
<l>kallār tiraṭōḷ kañcaṉaik kāyntāṉ pāyntāṉ kāḷiyaṉmēl</l>
<l>collār curuti muṟaiyōtic cōmuc ceyyun toḻiliṉōr</l>
<l>nallār maṟaiyōr palarvāḻum naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who raged against Kaṁsa with stone-like, strong shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">having desired [to go to] northern Mathurā,</l>
<l>To the bow festival, conquering the undesirable wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who leaped onto Kāliya,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where dwell many good people,</l>
<l rend="indent">Vedic experts,</l>
<l>[And] those with training who do the soma [rituals],</l>
<l rend="indent">correctly reciting the text-filled śruti [canon].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
